KSL Advisors, LLC Presents at 39th Annual NYU International Hospitality Industry Investment Conference 2017, Jun-04-2017 through Jun-06-2017
Jun 1 17
KSL Advisors, LLC Presents at 39th Annual NYU International Hospitality Industry Investment Conference 2017, Jun-04-2017 through Jun-06-2017. Venue: New York, United States. Presentation Date & Speakers: Jun-06-2017, Bernard N. Siegel, Partner, Eric C. Resnick, Co-Founder, Chief Executive Officer, and Managing Director, Gregory P. Kennealey, Director.


Belfry Golf Reportedly Up For Sale
May 18 17
De Vere Belfry Ltd. has been put up for sale with a £180 million price tag by KSL Capital Partners LLC, according to people with knowledge of the plan. Broker Jones Lang LaSalle Inc. has been appointed to advise on options for the Warwickshire estate, which includes a hotel and spa, the people said. Other options include selling a stake in the project. An executive from KSL Capital didn’t respond to an email sent on May 17, 2017, and a spokeswoman didn’t respond to calls and emails seeking comment. A spokeswoman for Jones Lang LaSalle declined to comment.


