 Career History



Associate

                                    2015 - Current                


KSL Advisors LLC


                  KSL Advisors makes investments in travel and leisure businesses, including the hospitality, recreation, clubs, real estate and travel services sectors. They focus on acquisitions of historically under-managed or under-capitalized businesses, striving to unlock hidden value by re-envisioning and repositioning these enterprises. Their approach involves closely managing each investment and expanding each enterprise across a broad array of complementary businesses in order to increase revenues and cash flows. The firm uses a variety of structural approaches in our investments, including complete ownership, joint ventures, minority interests and debt financing. Their targeted investment size is $25 million but they have the resources to invest up to $500 million.                




Analyst

                                    Prior - 2015                


Morgan Stanley & Co. International Plc


                  Morgan Stanley & Co. International Plc provides brokerage services. The firm provides financial investment services, including asset management services. The company was incorporated on October 28, 1986 and is headquartered in London, the United Kingdom.                





